ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Gas </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Co. </ORGANIZATION>, he and his partner, <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Jersey </LOCATION> oil man <PERSON> Leon </PERSON> <PERSON> Hess </PERSON>, own controlling interest in <ORGANIZATION> Lamar </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Life </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Corp. </ORGANIZATION>, a life insurance company which is the largest stockholder in <ORGANIZATION> Trustmark </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> National </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Bank </ORGANIZATION>, <LOCATION> Mississippi </LOCATION>'s second-largest financial institution <PERSON> Mark </PERSON> <PERSON> Dale </PERSON>, lead researcher for `` Unsolved Mysteries,'' <ORGANIZATION> NBC-TV </ORGANIZATION>'s series on unsolved crimes, said producers plan to broadcast a segment about the kidnapping this fall if Mrs. <PERSON> Hearin </PERSON> is not found Last year, the segments produced tips that led to the capture of nine fugitives and solving of eight cases.
